Technology: Prometheus + Grafana + Loki
Port: 3000:3000
Purpose: Observability & Metrics

Subcomponents:
  1. Prometheus (Port 9090)
     - Metrics collection
     - Time series database
     - Query engine
     
  2. Grafana (Port 3000)
     - Dashboard visualization
     - Alert management
     - User management
     
  3. Loki (Port 3100)
     - Log aggregation
     - Log querying
     - Label-based search

Monitored Metrics:
  - HTTP request duration
  - API request count
  - CPU/Memory usage
  - Database performance
  - FL training progress
  - Worker node status

Dashboards:
  - System Overview
  - API Performance
  - FL Status
  - Resource Utilization
  - Error Rate Analysis
  - Model Training Progress
